values:
Wow am I ever bored. Im so bored that I cleaned some of my house...me clean...scarey isnt it. I never clean house. I despise it!! But I really needed something 2 do...Im going crazy here!! At least David, Rena n Thomas are coming over later....then I wont b bored!! =) Speaking of Thomas...that lil fucker called me at 2:45 last night n woke me up! I was sound asleep. Wut did he have 2 ask me?...if I liked David...ud think that, that is kinda obvious...he was probably baked. If he wasnt I will have 2 kill him 4 being stupid. 2 make things worse I woke up at seven....SEVEN!!! Thats 4 days in a row Ive gotten up early on my own. I dont know wuts wrong with me...its summer I should b sleeping in!

Yesterday I had my first game in tha Golden Boy Tourny...we won 3-1. I played...the whole second half dont ya know. But Im paying 4 it now. I hurts just 2 walk. Charles isnt even here so I cant get him 2 do wut he does 2 make it feel better...I guess I could go 2 his replacement thats filling in 4 him while he's gone...but I dont trust her....dont ask me y cuz I could tell u...I just dont. I guess Ill just have 2 suffer till next friday.

2day was a shitty day. K actually this afternoon was okay...2night was shitty. I basically just watched tv 2day..u know lazed around n just relaxed. It was nice. Then I went 2 practice...it wasnt so great. I played a lil but my leg hurt n I had 2 sit down. I wish Charles had just said that I couldnt play...sure it would still b torture but it's worse now cuz I'm allowed 2 play but it hurts so I cant really. I cant explain why its worse but it just is...u would understand if you were going through it. I feel bad 4 complaining bout it cuz Chelsea's position is way worse...shes out all year. I would go nuts if I couldn't play soccer 4 that long. They would have to put me on drugz..no joke.

                  I got called 4 my in-car finally!!!

This Saturday is gonna b so much fun...cept 4 tha fact that Ive gotta get up @ 7:30 for my game which I wont play in much. But me, David, Thomas n Rena are all gonna do something...probably watch a movie at my house or wutever. It doesnt sound like nething special but its gonna b great. Im in like kiss denial...if theres such thing LoL. Ever since David kissed me while he was here n when he's around thats all I think about...it was really good! LoL. All I've gotta say is I hope tha second on is better...=)

Its Sunday n I didnt do very much 2day. I got 2 drive out 2 Gimili...that's right I drove...n had dinner with my grandparents. It was pretty boring. Nikki was being a brat 2 cuz shes scared of mosquitoes. Such a loser. Right now Im so sore...ive got a killer sun burn on my shoulders n it hurts!! I dont even have ne of that ice gel stuff either. It would b nice 2 have at the moment. I remember in grade 8....i think it was 8...newayz i remember when Rena got a really bad burn n she made me rub that stuff on her back till 2 in tha morning. It was so gross cuz at the end i had a layer of her skin on my hand. 

Right now theres shit all 2 do. I could study 4 pre-cal...but everybody knows I hate studying. Ill do it 2morrow inbetween getting stuck with needles...going 2 my soccer game...n getting my compression shorts. Damn...im sick of these busy days. 2day wasnt that busy but I didnt get 2 stay home n just relax. One day this week thats all im gonna do. Im determined!!!

Im kinda wishing a certain person would call me right now...

Well 2day I had my soccer car wash. I never want 2 wash another car again. She we made a lot of money but it was labor! N some of the customers were kinda bitchy. Nick n his friend Shane showed up just like they said they would. I have realized I only want 2 b Nicks friend...he kept touching me 2day n he was getting on my nerves. I put most of my energy into avoiding him. Liza talked 2 me as if nothing was different...which is good. She is appearently mad at me but is more sad. At least that's wut Chelsea says. Wutever I don't care. She'll eventually get over it.

Newayz thats enuff bout my love life...if u even wanna call it a love life. Right now im at my dad's new place. The house is pretty big. Cept its in this lil town..Ile De Chene or something like that. Its bout 10 minutes outside of city...kinda by the Mint. It's nice...but it's a lil 2 quiet 4 me. I gotta meet some ppl my age in this town. The good part bout him living here is that im finally gonna get the dirt bike he always promised me!! I cant wait till I get it. And next summer when I can drive on my own he said that I bring ppl with me here n we can camp out in the backyard n have a bon fire. The only thing is tho Ive gotta bring my own booze. LoL my dad is great..he doesnt really care if I drink n im not quite 18. Ah gonna have great timez next summer...but I better have great timez this summer. But now im out....outties!! LoL.

Well 2day didnt turn out as i thought it would. We were supposed 2 have a fun day shopping but it was pretty boring. There was a lil 2 much drama 4 me...I hope Nessa works everything out...she could do so much better. It was kinda weird...Jon came over here when Myra, Cotelle, Kaya n Ryan were here. Ive never really chilled with him b4...even tho he didnt say 2 much. Stupid Ryan made it obvious who i like so now Jon knows. He better not tell him. Im not 2 sure y it would b a bad thing...cuz then he would know...but i dunno. Nothing would happen so wutever.

                                     ...6 more dayz!!...

I feel so fresh n so clean right now. Just had a nice long hot shower.  It felt so good after a field hockey game n a soccer game.  Field hockey we won 2-1...i still gotta get a mouth guard lol. Soccer was fun...we play against guys year younger regional portage trail team....we got killed tho but its all good.  Stupid Derek tripped me n i landed in a puddle!!..haha...i got him back tho.  I love playing against the guys...they're so much more aggressive.

2day when i passed that certain person in the hall he gave looked at me not once but twice...oh ya. lol. It wasnt just a glance tho....it was a look.  Probably dont understand wut the hell i mean but thats alright....Rena saw she knows.  Remember baby steps.

                                         ..7 more dayz till minneapolis!!...

                                                           Luv Ya!!

                                                            - Sam -

2day was pretty crappy outside. I was so mad that it rained....I really wanted 2 play soccer. Then again I always want 2 play soccer lol. My day wasnt that bad tho...Josh bought me lunch so its all good =) OH!! and I made eye contact with him 2day...i dont think he saw my smile tho...it was kinda delayed.  I know big deal its only eye contact...WELL ITS A BIG DEAL 2 ME OKAY!!! Baby steps alright.

                               ...8 more dayz till I go 2 Minneapolis!!...

Wut the hell does exanimate mean?? lol

I am currently bored outta my fuckin mind. Theres nothing 4 me 2 do. I should b in bed cuz I gotta get up at 10:00...so early...4 practice but sleeping is no fun! lol n besides I couldnt sleep if I tried. AHHHHHH!!!!  I want something to do!!!

Newayz...I'll talk bout my day...which was just as boring as it is now. 2day I sat on my ass n watched tv....Fresh Prince of Belair is great haha. Ryan did come over n we watched a movie. Tha movie was alright...but it had a shitty ending!!

                                     OHHHHHHH!!!!

Ewwww!! Dimytry (dont kno how 2 spell his damn name) called me 2day.  I havent talked 2 him in almost a year n he just calls me out of no where. Kinda caught me off guard. Heres tha thing tho...he wants 2 do something 2morrow....oh I guess it wouldnt b 2morrow more like later 2day lol. I said mayb...he's calling me so I think I'll just go out...hopefully I can find something 2 do.

Ya I got nuttin else 2 say...LaTeR!!

Okay....I'm starting 2 get the hang of this thing. Ya I know its sad...it may not b that hard but I'm terrible with computers. I'll learn in time I guess. But its late so I'm gonna go 2 bed. NiGhT!!

                                                           **Sammie**
